ct binary systems, thereby\nproviding an unambiguous observational window for advanced LIGO to pin down the\nnature of dark matter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Jun 2017 16:13:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 Jun 2017 13:23:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 31 Jul 2017 02:17:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-18"}
