diately by proving that for a.e.~$t>0$, the\nquantity $\\ln (du(\\cdot,t))$ is bounded in $\\Omega$. In degenerate situations,\nthis particularly implies that the blow-up phenomena expressed in ($\\star$) in\nfact occur instantaneously.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Jun 2017 10:30:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-19"}
