es deviates\nslightly ($\\delta\\approx 1.293 \\pm 0.027$) from the linear behaviour in two\ndimensions. Analysis of local minima show that the pseudo ground states have\nsimilar structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Jun 2017 04:20:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Oct 2017 03:52:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-06"}
